                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-47-defend499 t18000528-47-punish266"></join>
               Fined 1s. and delivered to his serjeant
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
